# VulkanDesktop — test & smoke-run CLI

Full reference: [`Docs/CLI.md`](../../Docs/CLI.md). Implementation: `VulkanDesktop/Util/Util_EngineConfig.cpp`.

**Binary:** `x64\Debug\VulkanDesktop.exe` (after `MSBuild VulkanDesktop.sln /p:Configuration=Debug /p:Platform=x64`).

**Log:** `Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt` (repo root; fresh each run).

---

## Local verification (preferred)

Run from **repo root**. Use **`powershell`** (Windows PowerShell 5.1); scripts are `#Requires -Version 5.1`.

| Gate | Script | What it checks |
|------|--------|----------------|
| **G0** | `Scripts/Verify-CI.ps1` | MSBuild Debug\|x64, `Assert-ShaderDrift.ps1`, `GfxTests.exe` |
| **G0-smoke** | `Scripts/Verify-Smoke.ps1` | Built exe + `engine.json` + `sponza.json` + `Assert-SmokeLog.ps1` (**always `--no-validation`**) |
| **G0-validation** | Manual (see below) | Vulkan validation layers on; **no new `[VULKAN-VALIDATION]` ERROR** in log |

```powershell
powershell -File Scripts/Verify-CI.ps1
powershell -File Scripts/Verify-Smoke.ps1
```

**G0-smoke** requires a prior G0 build (`Verify-Smoke` does not rebuild). **Task close / vibe Closeout:** at minimum G0 + G0-smoke when GPU/runtime changed.

**G0-validation (required for RenderCore pass / barrier / descriptor / new compute or post-process work):** `Verify-Smoke.ps1` **does not** enable validation — passing G0-smoke alone can miss descriptor/barrier bugs that explode at runtime.

```powershell
$Repo = "<repo-root>"
& "$Repo\x64\Debug\VulkanDesktop.exe" `
  --asset-root $Repo `
  --config "$Repo\Config\engine.json" `
  --scene Data/Scenes/sponza.json `
  --validation --smoke-frames 120 --smoke-seconds 6
# Success: exit 0; tail Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt — no new [VULKAN-VALIDATION] at Error level
Select-String -Path "$Repo\Logs\engine_runtime_log.txt" -Pattern '\[VULKAN-VALIDATION\]' | Select-Object -Last 5
```

Use **`HybridDeferred`** preset (default in stress config) when exercising post-process / deferred paths. See `vulkan-render-pass-pitfalls.mdc` for common failure modes.

**Optional metrics:** `--perf-log Logs/perf_ci.jsonl` on VulkanDesktop (see `Docs/CLI.md`) then `Scripts/Perf-JsonlSummary.ps1`.

**CI / design:** [`Docs/Archived/plans/ci-verification_Plan.md`](../../Docs/Archived/plans/ci-verification_Plan.md). **GitHub:** `.github/workflows/vulkan-desktop.yml` mirrors G0 + soft GPU smoke.

