## Asset root (preferred)

**Agents / CI / odd cwd:** always pass explicit root — do not rely on cwd discovery alone.

`Verify-Smoke.ps1` passes `--asset-root <repo-root>` automatically. Manual runs:

```powershell
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --asset-root <repo-root> --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6
```

Local dev may still auto-discover repo root; automation must use `--asset-root` (`Docs/CLI.md`).

---

## When to use which command

| Goal | Command |
|------|---------|
| Full local G0 (agents, task close) | `powershell -File Scripts/Verify-CI.ps1` |
| GPU graceful smoke + log contract | `powershell -File Scripts/Verify-Smoke.ps1` |
| **RenderCore / pass changes (validation)** | Manual run with `--validation` (G0-validation above); **not** covered by Verify-Smoke |
| CLI parses, no GPU | `.\VulkanDesktop.exe --help` |
| Headless gfx contracts | `x64\Debug\GfxTests.exe` (included in Verify-CI) |
| Minimal scene | `--scene Data/Scenes/smoke.json` (optional; G0-smoke uses `sponza.json`) |
| Scene/manifest/path work | `--scene …` + `--asset-root <repo-root>` |
| CI/agent without validation layers | `--no-validation` |

---

## Graceful smoke (manual)

From `x64\Debug` (or use `Verify-Smoke.ps1`):

```powershell
Set-Location x64\Debug
.\VulkanDesktop.exe --asset-root <repo-root> --no-validation --smoke-seconds 6
```

Variants: `--scene Data/Scenes/demo.json` · `smoke.json` · `--smoke-frames 2` (fast; both thresholds apply if combined with `--smoke-seconds`).

### Success signals (tail log)

- `[CONFIG] assetRoot=…` under repo
- `[SCENE] LoadSceneResources completed`
- `[APP] Smoke dwell reached` · `[SCENE] UnloadScene` · `[APP] Engine exited run loop normally`
- Exit code **0**; no new `[ERROR]` on init (`--no-validation` OK)

`Verify-Smoke` also runs `Scripts/Assert-SmokeLog.ps1` on `Logs/engine_runtime_log.txt`.

